In [51]:
final_list = []
for i in  range(1,10):
    start_time = time.time()
    url = f"https://www.flipkart.com/search?q=mobile&sid=tyy%2C4io&as=on&as-show=on&otracker=AS_QueryStore_OrganicAutoSuggest_1_2_na_na_ps&otracker1=AS_QueryStore_OrganicAutoSuggest_1_2_na_na_ps&as-pos=1&as-type=HISTORY&suggestionId=mobile%7CMobiles&requestId=fd2f11a2-a618-4ec8-ae91-384250f6c1a2&page={i}"
    respone = requests.get(url)
    soup = BeautifulSoup(respone.text)
    
    for x in soup.find_all("div" , attrs={"class":"_2kHMtA"}):
        pname =  x.find("div" , attrs={"class":"_4rR01T"})
        cost =  x.find("div" , attrs={"class":"_30jeq3 _1_WHN1"})
        rating =  x.find("div" , attrs={"class":"_3LWZlK"})
        spec =  x.find_all("li" , attrs={"class":"rgWa7D"})
        spec = ";".join([i.text for i in spec])
        
        output_dict = {
            
            "product_name": None if pname is None else pname.text,
            "product_cost":  None if cost is None else cost.text,
            "product_rating": None if rating is None else rating.text,
            "product_spec": spec,
            "extracted_page" : i
            
        }
        
        final_list.append(output_dict)
    end_time= time.time()
    print(f"Scraped status  = {i} and time taken = {end_time - start_time}")
    time.sleep(1)
